<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">Desligue tecnologias sem fio não usadas</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents pagewide">
<p class="p">Pode reduzir o consumo de bateria desligando Bluetooth, Wi-Fi ou banda larga móvel que não estiverem sendo usadas.</p>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Open the <span class="gui"><a href="shell-introduction.html.pt#activities" title="Panorama de Atividades">Activities</a></span>
      overview and start typing <span class="gui">Wi-Fi</span> or <span class="gui">Bluetooth</span>, respectively.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Click <span class="gui">Wi-Fi</span> to open the panel, or <span class="gui">Bluetooth</span>, respectively.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">In the header bar, switch the unused services to off. Re-enable when needed by switching to on.</p></li>
</ol></div></div></div>
